GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_CoreNarratives> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_CoreNarratives> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#CoreNarratives> ;
    narr:childCount "23"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "fffddbaac7a15b84cb4ed77fb2c40cae638e650a" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of aswritten.ai’s competitive positioning, anchored by the thesis that [the next bottleneck is missing organizational context](narr:Position_WorldviewBottleneck). The core narrative relies on a [three-layer competitive model](narr:Position_ThreeLayerModel) comprising [knowledge extraction](narr:Narrative_CreationGap), [narrative ontology](narr:Narrative_ArchitectureGap), and [git-native infrastructure](narr:Narrative_InfrastructureGap). Recent technical and product shifts have refined how these layers manifest: [Salon is now defined as a per-memory capability](narr:Narrative_SalonAsCapability) rather than a deployment pattern, and [citations have moved to a constellation model](narr:Narrative_CiteConstellationModel) to better reflect historical changes. The operational workflow has also matured, moving toward a [Reviewable Worldview](narr:Narrative_ReviewableWorldview) that integrates capture, collaborative review, and merge cycles. Go-to-market strategies are actively pivoting, with a [decision to retire zero-context language](narr:Narrative_RetireZeroContext) and an ongoing re-evaluation of the [rigid two-call sales structure](narr:Narrative_HybridSalesMotion) in favor of a more fluid, background-extraction model.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AgenticCoherence> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ArchitectureGap> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_BetaFeedbackLoopIsSalon> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CiteConstellationModel> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CiteDeduplicationInvariant> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConsensusEngine> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CreationGap> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_HybridSalesMotion> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_InfrastructureGap> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_OrgKnowledgeAsCode> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_RetireZeroContext> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ReviewableWorldview> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SalonAsCapability> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_FundraisingStory> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_TwoCallStructure> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_TaxonomyRevision> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_AgenticBackPressure> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_ReviewableWorldviewSupersedesDemo1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_SalonIsPerMemory> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_ThreeLayerModel> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_WorldviewBottleneck> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_RuleOfThree_Layers> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "The most consequential organizational knowledge was never written down and cannot be retrieved — it must be extracted" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CreationGap> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Citations are constellations, not single claims" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CiteConstellationModel> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Organizational worldview as git-native code at the core of CI/CD enables agentic automations, multi-player contribution, and composable distribution" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_InfrastructureGap> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Salon is a per-memory capability, not a fifth deployment pattern" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SalonAsCapability> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "The Reviewable Worldview demo supersedes Demo 1 and shows the full product: capture, collaborative review, validation, and merge" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ReviewableWorldview> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The two-call sales structure is being challenged by a hybrid model that delivers value during the first call." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_HybridSalesMotion> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The 'Reviewable Worldview' demo is positioned as the primary product narrative, effectively demoting earlier demo iterations." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ReviewableWorldview> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_ReviewableWorldviewSupersedesDemo1> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Agentic coherence is framed as a critical technical bottleneck requiring self-verification, distinct from the broader organizational knowledge-as-code narrative." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AgenticCoherence> ] ;
    narr:writer "google/gemini-3.1-flash-lite" .
